{"type": "article", "id": 24608, "title": "像色票的巧克力包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-29T06:59:20Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 85, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606161039oeCEMamPbUkN058W.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这组巧克力包装有色票的感觉，打开盒子后从白色到黑色一共 6 块巧克力，中间是浅棕色到深棕色的过渡，简洁而有辨识度。每一块巧克力上面不忘写下对应的色号说明，很形象。西班牙平面设计公司 BLOCD. 想要设计圣诞节的礼品以送给客户，他们认为色票最能象征视觉设计。<a href=\"http://blocd.com/work/chocolate-pantone/\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606161037hIfkTrVcMJaz6Sdn.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606161038krt4AVsbnqIxlz5m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606161038ehGJnMRSkx6bpXNH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}